{"TopicId":41672,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"The Adventures Of The Big Flying Bus (And The Big Flying Bus mkII) (Pic heavy)","CreatedByName":"Sliinty","CreatedById":66232,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-08-08T21:38:25Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Sliinty","CreatedById":66232,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-08-08T21:38:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ESo recently I made a bus in ksp\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/OroKhuv.png\u0022 alt=\u0022OroKhuv.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAfter attaching jets to it to drive faster I started thinking kerbal, \u0022can I put wings on it and make it fly?\u0022 \u0022Yes, yes I can.\u0022\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/NvAfLD9.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022NvAfLD9.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EA little help from some rocket engines to kick the nose up and we\u0027re in the air, flying gracefully in exactly the way bricks do not. Bill\u0027s enjoying it anyway.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/I2e3zlF.png\u0022 alt=\u0022I2e3zlF.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/V3fM2ZY.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022V3fM2ZY.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ETime to prank people by putting a bus somewhere in which they would not expect to find one!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/mPaGHG8.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022mPaGHG8.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYou know where we\u0027re headed.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/voPdNYN.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022voPdNYN.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EComing in to land. If you\u0027re wondering whether it flies well I can tell you confidently that at the time of writing it is the easiest bus to fly that has ever been made.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/BQHbdHL.png\u0022 alt=\u0022BQHbdHL.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EErr... Bill?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EToo bad. Announcing the mkII!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/uQsi8Jg.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022uQsi8Jg.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENow with parachutes.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/wWV6Gdf.png\u0022 alt=\u0022wWV6Gdf.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI forgot to mention that the wings detach. Anyway from the lack of another screenie I think you can figure out whether it landed on flat ground or 60 degree incline for yourself.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-decoration:underline;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003EWill the B.F.B. return???!!!!! Who knows!\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-08-08T21:40:58Z\u0022 title=\u002208/08/2013 09:40  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 8, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by Sliinty\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NASI Director","CreatedById":64746,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-08-09T01:08:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYou should sell that patent to Airbus. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027ll escort my pun and I out now.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Valley","CreatedById":73883,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-08-09T02:11:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E*Whips out a tape recorder* \u0022Note to self. Design flying buses to carry Hanland assault groups to planet\u0027s surface. Make them yellow and have Magic School Bus Theme pumped out of speakers to confuse the anti-aircraft crews as they land.\u0022\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-08-09T02:31:29Z\u0022 title=\u002208/09/2013 02:31  AM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 9, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by Valley\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mekan1k","CreatedById":48750,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-08-10T09:01:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EMagic school bus!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"IndieDev3D","CreatedById":67725,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-08-10T11:06:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAbsolutely brilliant, well done!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CvVtjRtb","CreatedById":59454,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-08-18T05:29:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n[]\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-08-02T01:10:51Z\u0022 title=\u002208/02/2019 01:10  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 2, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by CvVtjRtb\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}